      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality specimen that has been meticulously maintained. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or aging. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did the day it left the factory, with all systems functioning perfectly and a comprehensive service history included. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives like new, perfect for a discerning collector or someone who demands perfection.",
