    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved over the years. Perfect for someone looking for a reliable, smooth journey without the brand-new price tag. You\u2019re going to love how it handles! Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 33500.0,
