    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E92 M3 powered by the high-revving 4.0L S65B40 V8, an engine renowned for its eight individual throttle bodies and 8,400 RPM redline. This specimen features a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated M-variable differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement with VAC treated shells and upgraded throttle actuators to ensure long-term reliability of the double-VANOS system. The chassis retains its structural rigidity with no signs of subframe stress, and the Electronic Damping Control (EDC) provides precise rebound and compression adjustments. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its 'good' status, the drivetrain remains in peak operational form for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Clean title. All maintenance records available. Runs smoothly. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
