      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and value, having been maintained with a focus on longevity. The exterior paint still holds a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor surface scratches and small stone chips on the lower valance typical of careful daily use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the upholstery is free of tears or heavy bolsters wear, and the dashboard remains crack-free. All electronic features, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. It has received regular synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the most recent service included a comprehensive multi-point inspection, new air filters, and a coolant flush. The tires have roughly 70% tread remaining, and the transmission shifts through all gears seamlessly. This is a well-documented, honest car ready for its next long-term owner.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
