    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of BMW\u2019s S54-powered icon. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features a recently serviced VANOS system and updated rod bearings, ensuring valvetrain longevity and peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcements to manage torsional stress during spirited cornering. Power is managed via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential. The suspension features refreshed bushings and upgraded dampers for optimized damping rebound and compression. While displaying minor cosmetic patina consistent with an enthusiast-driven vehicle, this M3 is technically sound, offering a pure analog driving experience with a linear power band and exceptional throttle response.",
